name: Winged Things
description:
12 year old NFT artist Footlong hand painted this artwork and then edited it on Photoshop with her art mentor.  Footlong lives in the heart of France with her spouse and 3 kids where her favorite pastimes are mud wrestling and making hearty sandwiches for  Eiffel Tower visitors in the spring.

This NFT was made for the #Fool4TEZ event, a Tezos community wide April Fools event hosted by @TerosEso @strtsomethingio @_xs @Tery & @rblbab

For questions about this artist please contact art mentor, Lily White @rblbab
